Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.42,0:00:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演即將進入高潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.52,0:00:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exelion進駐宇宙才藝慶祝大會 讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著輪到令人矚目的太田教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與他合唱的人是 傳說中的玫瑰女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野和美小姐親自欽點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.90,0:00:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿著外遇的氣息 歌名是“男與女的愛情遊戲”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.70,0:00:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就請兩位上臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.31,0:00:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不太好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.41,0:00:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.55,0:00:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 好親熱喔 人家會燙傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.92,0:00:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.75,0:00:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家會喝過頭都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.49,0:00:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱女子真是令人疼惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.86,0:00:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練 笑一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.00,0:00:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家會喝過頭都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.83,0:00:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的你總是愛逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.90,0:01:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.14,0:01:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著我不想讓你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.25,0:01:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰水割酒擦身而過陳舊傷痛
