Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀美子 紀美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀美子你過得好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的好朋友法子 現在正在銀河中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.79,0:03:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽變得好小 混在銀河之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.39,0:03:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經看不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我用精神感應傳給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.20,0:03:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀美子 你能相信 宇宙船竟會如此搖晃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.04,0:03:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它以時速數十億公里 這麼快的速度在飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.81,0:03:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在幾乎真空的宇宙中 感覺像是迎著風前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在同一個宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.45,0:04:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些地方狂風不止 有些地方則是風平浪靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.69,0:04:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在真正的海上航行似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方已保留0.5秒差距加速空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以進行WARP
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 全艦進行WARP
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦進行WARP
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.30,0:04:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WARP要在真正 寧靜的海中才能進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.51,0:04:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著會進入亞空間 這時候很壯觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.84,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙太會電漿化（Plasma） 那真的很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.75,0:04:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我只看過一次 因為進行WARP時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.22,0:04:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一定要回到自己房間待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.92,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入亞空間後一定會做的事 就是講鬼故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.79,0:04:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的亞空間 是與靈界相通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.86,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而死者的靈魂為了尋找親人 會徘徊在走廊或是停機坪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.44,0:04:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 偶爾會聽到 敲打待命室的敲擊聲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然對這種事不討厭 但是卻很害怕聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後最後一定會玩試膽遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.59,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼可能… 拜託 有誰能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不想被人看笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是來試膽的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 我的臉有那麼可怕嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到女生宿舍也做著同樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把記號放著 然後回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.46,0:06:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真有那麼嚇人嗎？ 頭帶拿來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那上面吧？ 我去幫你掛就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.28,0:06:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟人 這樣也算是宇宙戰士嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然嚇到腳軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WARP中應該是 第二級警戒待命狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.93,0:07:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WARP結束後 兩人都穿上太空裝到我房間報到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.08,0:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次被叫來擦雷射炮的鏡片時 我還在當海軍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.72,0:07:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大的星雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為距離近而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.02,0:07:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空好亮喔 這邊可以看到好多氣體星雲耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有很多老化的星星吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 像花一樣耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是星星的死體啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.78,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點感性也沒有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.45,0:07:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 腰好痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.68,0:07:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全艦 航線不變 速度不變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.09,0:08:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 這樣下去 今天就能通過LEAF64恒星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.96,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LEAF64啊… 真是令人懷念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次來時我還在當太空人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它非常的像太陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.34,0:08:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮喔 猶如宇宙中的綠洲一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.45,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像太陽一般年輕的星球 真的是很少見呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.82,0:08:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽型的重力干擾很小 真的很方便作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.39,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的銀河中 大概只有數字的星星吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航線12點鐘方向 有多數物體接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對速度接近光速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 換下個鏡片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.14,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.04,0:08:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.49,0:09:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵軍 以2萬公里的速度擦身而過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 追擊敵人 全艦全速變更航線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.17,0:09:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用恒星LEAF64的 重力場進行回轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.54,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官 開始準備重力回轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.21,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全艦隊 準備集合 地點由你決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.11,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體艦隊 艦隊集合準備 集合座標120 717 341
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊集合準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力回轉準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各艦間距變更為2公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從第一到第三開始作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙戰機V開始組裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.07,0:09:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子魚雷裝填準備 第四安全裝置以前全部解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.14,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三到第六補助引擎 開始運轉 出力80%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.71,0:10:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦即將進入 第一級戰鬥待命狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.28,0:10:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20小時後與敵人遭遇 預定時間為明晨4時30分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.76,0:10:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是女子更衣室前 女子更衣室前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.36,0:10:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…左邊的紅色警告出現時 先讓空間陀螺儀固定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再關閉連動裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.93,0:10:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊的紅色警告出現時 要把進氣閥調到30
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 原來你這麼用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.71,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最起碼也得將宇宙的基本動作模式背起來才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我落後了人家好幾個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西在實戰時是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.95,0:10:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 幹嘛用學長的口氣訓我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.39,0:10:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概因為你是可愛的學妹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先跟你說清楚 我跟姊姊的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在TOP部隊中算是最棒的一組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.03,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣連夥伴也沒有 完全單打獨鬥的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法體會的辛苦可多著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.51,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長口氣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你聽說了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說佐江子昨天 跟她男朋友做到C了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那兩個人真的做了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.75,0:11:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又在床上撞到了頭 真是好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你看法子 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LEAF64
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是LEAF64？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼醜陋的紅色巨星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.91,0:11:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據星座絕對座標 這是無庸置疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.02,0:11:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是銀河系英仙座旋臂 第八分支 恒星LEAF64
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.36,0:11:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LEAF64跟太陽一樣 是年輕的白色恒星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.16,0:12:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不過十數年 就起了這樣的變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？說來聽聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.42,0:12:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若左方有反應延遲時 消除的方法是像這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 搞不懂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要讓高屋上陣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以她的能力來說 這太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這由我來判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.67,0:12:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 身為搭檔的我 已經覺得無法和她一起戰鬥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.21,0:12:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我不打算換掉高屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.52,0:12:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？那從今天起 我要解除與法子的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果法子是我的搭檔 我無法與敵人作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是為了你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高屋 我發現了你的潛力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我讓你與天野組成一組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我認為 你們可以成為最棒的拍檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.05,0:13:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人只要少了一人 一切的努力都會化成灰燼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.43,0:13:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你所具有的可能性 你也要相信自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.20,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 磨練自己 將你的堅持讓我瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.04,0:14:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 教科書不見了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.71,0:14:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.95,0:14:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也變成一個人了 因為姊姊已經在討厭我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.52,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法 因為一開始我們水準就差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你變成一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.57,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我一起搭檔？ 我現在剛好也在找夥伴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以 怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這麼說定 你知道我的名字嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫史密斯•多連
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.18,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫高屋法子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛笑啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去登記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.87,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間接親嘴 討厭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.34,0:15:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tarzion回轉完成 與敵方部隊接觸還有25分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍確認 距離221光秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接觸地點預計為 第五行星軌道附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.65,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮門開啟 準備進行雷射炮射擊戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.49,0:15:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮門開啟 準備進行雷射炮射擊戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.63,0:15:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位盤運作開始 光子魚雷發射管開啟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.53,0:15:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非戰鬥人員到第三區待命 TOP部隊快準備出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.04,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦載機出動後 TOP部隊會被發射至敵軍部隊前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.64,0:15:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後由各組自行判斷行動 各機間距保持1000公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.92,0:15:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要在時間內使用然後返航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.92,0:15:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,californium核子彈頭的半衰期是三小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要遵守返航命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是史上第一次的 機械兵器部隊作戰行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.33,0:16:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都要謹慎行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.50,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械人彈射軌道全部開啟 抽氣中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.49,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOP部隊出發準備完成 第二雷射炮區 準備完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.52,0:16:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子魚雷裝填完成 各主炮自動追蹤裝置設定完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.46,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標時差1.8光秒 確認命中時間預定3.6秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.47,0:16:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮門射擊！ 280秒後艦載機與TOP部隊出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 準備出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.64,0:18:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我在你的下方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯 我看不到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.61,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 放心吧 敵人還沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 我負責攻 你負責守 知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我負責掩護你是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.60,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tarzion被擊中 嚴重受創…不 要沉沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 衝擊波要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有5秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.05,0:19:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.05,0:19:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 放心吧 這樣還不會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.19,0:19:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敵人 在左上方 有兩台過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.20,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞到右邊去了 可惡 新的又來了 在左上方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.07,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到右邊去的傢伙拜託你了 瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.11,0:20:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯 回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.72,0:20:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我討厭這樣 史密斯 史密斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 敵人的主體在LEAF64
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.37,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們至今接觸的敵方部隊 並非主力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誘餌嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.71,0:20:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且敵人又在LEAF64 開始集結了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.04,0:20:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 通知全艦 將在外面的部隊回收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收後立刻進行WARP
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.95,0:20:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.15,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說敵人會在恒星產卵 並使其孵化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.12,0:21:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 那與在這一帶 常發生恒星爆炸有關？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.66,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真是這樣 那我們得 儘快離開這個星域才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.10,0:22:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一發都沒發射
