Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.42,0:23:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.15,0:23:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…史密斯他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.63,0:23:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時跟史密斯在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.16,0:23:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻什麼也沒有做… 什麼也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.34,0:23:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.14,0:24:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.41,0:24:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練 我什麼都願意做 我要鍛煉自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.01,0:24:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 請對我嚴格督促
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.18,0:24:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定得做到 讓姊姊認同我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.78,0:24:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
